    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "format-body",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 175,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 260,
      "text": "STRUCTURE (30-45 sec):\n\n1. HOOK (0-3s): Curiosity gap + visual pattern interrupt\n   \"There's a molecule in your body that quietly controls\n    how much energy you have...\"\n\n2. EDUCATION (3-20s): Science breakdown, simplified\n   Coenzyme in every cell → energy → DNA repair → aging\n\n3. BENEFITS (20-28s): Rapid-fire benefit stack\n   Energy + Focus + Metabolism + Sleep + Anti-aging\n\n4. REVEAL (28-30s): Name the peptide/molecule\n   \"The molecule we're talking about is NAD+\"\n\n5. CTA (30-34s): Comment trigger for DM automation\n   \"Comment NAD+ and I'll send you more info\"",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STRUCTURE (30-45 sec):\n\n1. HOOK (0-3s): Curiosity gap + visual pattern interrupt\n   \"There's a molecule in your body that quietly controls\n    how much energy you have...\"\n\n2. EDUCATION (3-20s): Science breakdown, simplified\n   Coenzyme in every cell → energy → DNA repair → aging\n\n3. BENEFITS (20-28s): Rapid-fire benefit stack\n   Energy + Focus + Metabolism + Sleep + Anti-aging\n\n4. REVEAL (28-30s): Name the peptide/molecule\n   \"The molecule we're talking about is NAD+\"\n\n5. CTA (30-34s): Comment trigger for DM automation\n   \"Comment NAD+ and I'll send you more info\"",
