      "id": "visual-body",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 275,
      "text": "TALKING HEAD (bottom 40% of frame):\n- Doctor in branded scrubs/polo (logo visible)\n- Lav mic clipped on — professional audio\n- Direct eye contact, confident delivery\n- Subtle hand gestures for emphasis\n\nROTATING B-ROLL (top 60% of frame):\n- Scene changes every 2-4 seconds\n- Stock/custom footage matching the topic:\n  Syringes & vials, DNA helixes, cellular imagery,\n  patients receiving treatment, lifestyle shots\n  (sleeping, exercising, focused at desk)\n\nTEXT OVERLAYS:\n- Bold white text with shadow, synced to speech\n- 2-4 words max per overlay (keyword emphasis)\n- Centered bottom third, below B-roll\n\nPACING: Fast cuts (2-3s each), no dead air",
