    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "pillar4a-body",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 813,
      "width": 490,
      "height": 165,
      "text": "\"Day in the life of a peptide clinic\"\n  → Show consults, pharmacy deliveries, patient check-ins\n\"How we ship your peptides\" → fulfillment process, cold chain\n\"Meet our medical director\" → trust-building, credentials\n\"Inside our compounding pharmacy partner\" → quality/trust\n\"Patient Q&A session\" → answer real DMs on camera\n\"Unboxing a patient's peptide kit\" → what arrives at your door\n\"How I read your bloodwork\" → lab review walkthrough\n\"Our telehealth consult process\" → screen recording of flow",
