    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "hooks-body",
      "x": 610,
      "y": 813,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 165,
      "text": "\"There's a molecule in your body that...\" (curiosity gap)\n\"Doctors don't want you to know this\" (controversy)\n\"I gave this to 100 patients. Here's what happened\" (data)\n\"Stop taking [common supplement] — do this instead\" (contrarian)\n\"You're aging faster than you should. Here's why\" (fear/urgency)\n\"The peptide that heals like Wolverine\" (pop culture analogy)\n\"3 signs your NAD+ levels are crashing\" (self-diagnosis)\n\"This is what $400/month of peptides looks like\" (transparency)\n\"POV: Your first peptide consult\" (experiential)\n\"The weight loss injection no one talks about\" (insider)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"There's a molecule in your body that...\" (curiosity gap)\n\"Doctors don't want you to know this\" (controversy)\n\"I gave this to 100 patients. Here's what happened\" (data)\n\"Stop taking [common supplement] — do this instead\" (contrarian)\n\"You're aging faster than you should. Here's why\" (fear/urgency)\n\"The peptide that heals like Wolverine\" (pop culture analogy)\n\"3 signs your NAD+ levels are crashing\" (self-diagnosis)\n\"This is what $400/month of peptides looks like\" (transparency)\n\"POV: Your first peptide consult\" (experiential)\n\"The weight loss injection no one talks about\" (insider)",
