    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cta-body",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 1078,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "COMMENT TRIGGER (highest engagement — like @doctorjarrett):\n  \"Comment [PEPTIDE NAME] and I'll send you more info\"\n  → ManyChat or ChatAutomate DM automation\n  → Auto-sends link to booking page or quiz\n\nLINK IN BIO:\n  → Linktree or custom page with:\n    - Free peptide guide (email capture)\n    - \"Which peptide is right for you?\" quiz\n    - Book a consult button\n    - Program pricing page\n\nSTORIES → SWIPE UP / LINK STICKER:\n  → Direct to booking page for warm leads\n  → Poll stickers: \"Have you tried peptides? Yes / Not yet\"\n  → Question box: \"Ask me anything about peptides\"",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "COMMENT TRIGGER (highest engagement — like @doctorjarrett):\n  \"Comment [PEPTIDE NAME] and I'll send you more info\"\n  → ManyChat or ChatAutomate DM automation\n  → Auto-sends link to booking page or quiz\n\nLINK IN BIO:\n  → Linktree or custom page with:\n    - Free peptide guide (email capture)\n    - \"Which peptide is right for you?\" quiz\n    - Book a consult button\n    - Program pricing page\n\nSTORIES → SWIPE UP / LINK STICKER:\n  → Direct to booking page for warm leads\n  → Poll stickers: \"Have you tried peptides? Yes / Not yet\"\n  → Question box: \"Ask me anything about peptides\"",
