    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "funnel-body",
      "x": 640,
      "y": 1078,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "REEL (reach: 10-100K views)\n  ↓ Comment trigger / profile visit\nDM AUTOMATION (ManyChat)\n  ↓ Sends quiz link or guide\nLEAD MAGNET (\"Which Peptide Is Right For You?\")\n  ↓ Captures email + phone\nEMAIL NURTURE (3-5 email sequence)\n  ↓ Education → social proof → CTA\nBOOK CONSULT ($0 or $49 intro consult)\n  ↓ Video call with NP/PA\nLABS + Rx + SHIP\n  ↓ Patient onboarded\nSUBSCRIPTION ($299-499/mo recurring)\n\nConversion: ~1-3% of reel viewers → lead\n            ~20-30% of leads → consult\n            ~50-70% of consults → patient",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "REEL (reach: 10-100K views)\n  ↓ Comment trigger / profile visit\nDM AUTOMATION (ManyChat)\n  ↓ Sends quiz link or guide\nLEAD MAGNET (\"Which Peptide Is Right For You?\")\n  ↓ Captures email + phone\nEMAIL NURTURE (3-5 email sequence)\n  ↓ Education → social proof → CTA\nBOOK CONSULT ($0 or $49 intro consult)\n  ↓ Video call with NP/PA\nLABS + Rx + SHIP\n  ↓ Patient onboarded\nSUBSCRIPTION ($299-499/mo recurring)\n\nConversion: ~1-3% of reel viewers → lead\n            ~20-30% of leads → consult\n            ~50-70% of consults → patient",
