    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "tools-body",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 1368,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "FILMING: iPhone 15 Pro + lav mic + ring light + teleprompter app\nEDITING: CapCut (free) or Descript (AI captions + editing)\nB-ROLL: Artgrid, Storyblocks, or custom clinic footage\nCAPTIONS: CapCut auto-captions (bold, centered, animated)\nSCHEDULING: Later, Planoly, or Meta Business Suite\nDM AUTOMATION: ManyChat ($15/mo) — comment triggers\nANALYTICS: Instagram Insights + Metricool for cross-platform\nBATCHING: Film 8-10 reels in one session (2-3 hrs/week)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
