    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "kpi-body",
      "x": 640,
      "y": 1368,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "Month 1-2:  500-2K followers, 5-10K avg reel views\nMonth 3-4:  2-5K followers, 10-30K avg views, 50+ leads/mo\nMonth 5-6:  5-15K followers, 30-100K views, 100+ leads/mo\nMonth 7-12: 15-50K followers, viral potential, 200+ leads/mo\n\nTRACK WEEKLY:\n- Reel views, saves (intent signal), shares, comments\n- Profile visits → link clicks → leads captured\n- Cost per lead (organic vs paid boost)\n- Comment-to-DM conversion rate (ManyChat)\n- Lead-to-consult-to-patient conversion rate",
      "fontSize": 13,
