    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "caption-body",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 1598,
      "width": 814.5921630859375,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "CAPTION FORMAT (like @doctorjarrett): Long-form educational caption (150-300 words) that expands on the reel's topic.\nStart with a hook line. Include scientific context. End with CTA: \"Comment [KEYWORD] below\" + location + contact + website.\n\nHASHTAGS (15-20 per post, mix of sizes):\nBroad (1M+): #Wellness #Longevity #AntiAging #WeightLoss #Biohacking #HealthyLiving #Peptides\nMid (100K-1M): #PeptideTherapy #NAD #CellularHealth #CellularEnergy #HormoneOptimization #Semaglutide #Tirzepatide\nNiche (<100K): #BPC157 #GHKCu #Sermorelin #PeptideStack #CompoundingPharmacy #TelehealthDoctor #PeptideClinic\nLocal: #[City]Wellness #[City]Doctor #[State]Health",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
